<section>
    <h2>Cardio Training</h2>
    <p>Try brisk walking, jogging, cycling, or dancing 15-20 minutes, 3 times per week.</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Strength Training</h2>
    <p>Push-ups, squats, lunges, and planks. Do 3 sets of each exercise.</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Flexibility & Recovery</h2>
    <p>Stretch daily for 10-15 minutes to improve mobility and prevent injuries.</p>
</section>

